com.amalgam.app

类 DialogFragmentUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amalgam.app.DialogFragmentUtils

  • public final class DialogFragmentUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility for DialogFragment and DialogFragment. Operations for the support library version of DialogFragment has a method name prefix as "support".

        public static <F extends android.app.DialogFragment> F findDialogFragmentByTag(android.app.FragmentManager manager,
                                                                               java.lang.String tag)
        查找对应tag名的fragment Find fragment registered on the manager.
        类型参数:
        F - the dialog fragment impl.
        参数:
        manager - the manager.
        tag - the tag string that is related to the DialogFragment.
        返回:
        the DialogFragment. null if the fragment not found.
